        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Estimated value. Adobe bricks are used in the construction sector in several regions of the world (Middle East, Western Asia, North Africa, West Africa, South America, southwestern North America, Southwestern and Eastern Europe). Nonetheless, an estimation of the annual global production volume through the GDP would overestimate the production amount. Therefore, the production volume of Ecuador (original dataset) is used to estimate the global production volume. A factor of 10 is assumed. </productionVolumeComment>
        <classification classificationId="39b0f0ab-1a2f-401b-9f4d-6e39400760a4">
